1
00:01:27,232 --> 00:01:29,088
[GASP]

2
00:01:35,988 --> 00:01:38,554
- JUST THINK OF IT
AS A HIDING PLACE.

3
00:01:38,588 --> 00:01:41,288
I'LL EVEN COME BACK
AND DIG YOU UP,

4
00:01:41,321 --> 00:01:42,254
IF I REMEMBER.

5
00:01:42,288 --> 00:01:47,154
- DO YOU PROMISE?
DO YOU SWEAR NOT TO FORGET?

6
00:01:53,298 --> 00:01:55,898
[DOG BARKING]

7
00:01:59,531 --> 00:02:03,098
- COME ON.
DON'T TELL ME
YOU BELIEVE HER STORY.

8
00:02:03,131 --> 00:02:04,031
- HMM.

9
00:02:04,064 --> 00:02:06,798
- BUT IT IS TRUE!
KAGOME FELL DOWN THE WELL,

10
00:02:06,831 --> 00:02:09,331
AND THEN A MONSTER CAME UP
AND KIDNAPPED HER.

11
00:02:09,364 --> 00:02:12,598
- THERE IS A CERTAIN LEGEND
OF THE BONE EATER'S WELL.

12
00:02:12,631 --> 00:02:15,364
SINCE ANCIENT DAYS,
WHATEVER'S INSIDE

13
00:02:15,398 --> 00:02:17,798
HAS CONSUMED THE CORPSES
OF MONSTERS.

14
00:02:17,831 --> 00:02:20,564
BUT WHAT IF THE CONTINUUM
OF TIME-SPACE

15
00:02:20,598 --> 00:02:22,531
IS ITSELF DISRUPTED?

16
00:02:27,564 --> 00:02:29,498
- [MEOW]

17
00:02:32,331 --> 00:02:36,098
- THAT'LL STOP YA.
[CHUCKLES]

18
00:02:36,131 --> 00:02:36,998
[WHIRRING]

19
00:02:37,031 --> 00:02:38,764
- CLOSED IT OFF?
- YUP.

20
00:02:38,798 --> 00:02:42,864
WE NEEDN'T WORRY ABOUT ANY MORE
VISITORS FROM THERE.

21
00:02:42,898 --> 00:02:46,964
I USED SPECIAL SPIRIT WARDS
JUST IN CASE.

22
00:02:46,998 --> 00:02:49,364
- HMM.

23
00:02:52,864 --> 00:02:54,831
- UHH.
[SNIFFING]

24
00:02:54,864 --> 00:02:59,098
THAT'S HER, ALL RIGHT.
I'D KNOW HER ANYWHERE.

25
00:03:03,464 --> 00:03:05,198
WHY'D SHE LEAVE HER CLOTHES?

26
00:03:05,231 --> 00:03:09,164
SHE DID IT.
SHE WENT BACK TO HER OWN WORLD.

27
00:03:09,198 --> 00:03:13,698
THROUGH HERE, WAS IT?
UHH.

28
00:03:18,731 --> 00:03:21,498
[DOG BARKING]

29
00:03:22,064 --> 00:03:26,198
- AHH, IT'S SO GOOD TO BE HOME
IN MY OWN BED.

30
00:03:26,231 --> 00:03:32,164
WAS I REALLY THERE,
IN THAT WEIRD FEUDAL JAPAN?

31
00:03:39,198 --> 00:03:41,764
- ONLY BY WORKING TOGETHER
WILL THE 2 OF YE

32
00:03:41,798 --> 00:03:45,764
BE ABLE TO RECOVER THE SHARDS
OF THE JEWEL.

33
00:03:47,831 --> 00:03:53,864
- OH, YOU NAUGHTY, NAUGHTY GIRL.
YOU SHATTERED THE JEWEL.

34
00:03:53,898 --> 00:03:57,464
AND WHAT ABOUT THE GIRL,
THE ONE WITH THE HAIR?

35
00:03:57,498 --> 00:04:02,131
WHAT DID SHE WANT?
DUH, THE JEWEL, OF COURSE.

36
00:04:02,164 --> 00:04:05,631
[SIGH]
WHAT IF SHE WON'T GIVE IT BACK?

37
00:04:05,664 --> 00:04:07,531
I CAN ALREADY HEAR INUYASHA.

38
00:04:07,564 --> 00:04:10,864
- I NEVER ASKED FOR YOUR HELP.
GO HOME.

39
00:04:10,898 --> 00:04:12,598
YOU ONLY SLOW ME DOWN, ANYWAY.

40
00:04:12,631 --> 00:04:17,531
- HA. THAT'S RIGHT.
OH, WHAT AM I WORRYING
ABOUT HIM FOR?

41
00:04:17,564 --> 00:04:20,431
THAT'S IT, THEN.
CHAPTER CLOSED.

42
00:04:20,464 --> 00:04:24,364
- AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,
IT WAS JUST A FAIRY TALE.

43
00:04:24,398 --> 00:04:26,698
- KAGOME, IT'S DINNERTIME,

44
00:04:26,731 --> 00:04:28,798
PLUS, YOUR FRIEND'S
ON THE PHONE.

45
00:04:28,831 --> 00:04:31,031
- COMING!
- [MEOW]

46
00:04:31,064 --> 00:04:35,964
- GRANDPA, THOSE THINGS
WILL STAY ON, RIGHT?

47
00:04:35,998 --> 00:04:41,331
- 'COURSE THEY WILL.
HAVE A LITTLE FAITH, WILL YOU?

48
00:04:41,364 --> 00:04:44,164
- IF THERE'S ONE THING I KNOW,
IT'S SPIRITS.

49
00:04:44,198 --> 00:04:49,231
- AHH! REAL FOOD, REAL FOOD...
- I'LL DEFEND YOU
TO MY LAST BREATH, KAGOME,

50
00:04:49,264 --> 00:04:53,964
SO DON'T YOU WORRY.
- I DON'T THINK SHE HEARD YOU.

51
00:04:53,998 --> 00:04:54,831
- [SOBBING]

52
00:04:54,864 --> 00:04:58,764
- AHH, WHAT A WONDERFUL TIME
TO BE ALIVE.

53
00:04:59,531 --> 00:05:02,031
OH, I CAN'T WAIT TO--

54
00:05:07,264 --> 00:05:09,198
- I--INUYASHA?

55
00:05:09,231 --> 00:05:12,731
- IDIOT!
WHO TOLD YOU YOU COULD GO HOME?

56
00:05:12,764 --> 00:05:15,364
- UH--WHAT--UH, WHERE DID YOU--

57
00:05:15,398 --> 00:05:16,998
- THROUGH THE WELL, OF COURSE!

58
00:05:17,031 --> 00:05:19,731
- THE WELL?
BUT THE WELL IS--

59
00:05:19,764 --> 00:05:20,464
- YOU LIE!

60
00:05:20,498 --> 00:05:22,731
I MADE THOSE
SPIRIT WARDS MYSELF.

61
00:05:22,764 --> 00:05:23,898
THERE'S NO WAY YOU COULD HAVE--

62
00:05:23,931 --> 00:05:26,264
- WELL, I HATE TO BREAK IT
TO YOU, OLD MAN,

63
00:05:26,298 --> 00:05:29,564
BUT THEY DON'T WORK.
- [SCREAMING]

64
00:05:29,598 --> 00:05:30,764
- GRANDPA.

65
00:05:30,798 --> 00:05:34,064
- COME ON, YOU.
WE'RE LEAVING.
- NO, AND YOU CAN'T MAKE ME.

66
00:05:34,098 --> 00:05:35,331
- STAY RIGHT THERE.

67
00:05:35,364 --> 00:05:37,598
- NOW WHAT?
- MOM, I--

68
00:05:37,631 --> 00:05:39,864
- YOUR EARS.
ARE THEY REAL?

69
00:05:39,898 --> 00:05:42,531
- ME NEXT!
ME NEXT!
- UH, MOM,

70
00:05:42,564 --> 00:05:43,964
THAT'S NOT REALLY COOL.

71
00:05:43,998 --> 00:05:46,731
THOUGH I DID IT, TOO, BUT...

72
00:05:47,264 --> 00:05:50,098
INUYASHA, DO YOU SEE THAT?

73
00:05:50,131 --> 00:05:52,564
- I DON'T SEE NOTHIN.'

74
00:05:52,598 --> 00:05:56,531
- A HAIR.
ON YOUR SHOULDER, SEE?

75
00:05:59,198 --> 00:06:00,231
[GASP]
IT MOVED.

76
00:06:00,264 --> 00:06:03,231
- KAGOME, YOUR HAND.
- WHAT IS IT?

77
00:06:03,264 --> 00:06:05,098
- IT'S HERE.
[GASP]

78
00:06:05,131 --> 00:06:06,798
ONLY I CAN SEE IT.

79
00:06:06,831 --> 00:06:09,498
- BUT SEEING ALONE
IS NOT ENOUGH.

80
00:06:09,531 --> 00:06:13,464
[GASP]
- THAT GIRL WITH THE HAIR.
YURA.

81
00:06:13,498 --> 00:06:15,364
OH, NO.

82
00:06:18,264 --> 00:06:20,264
[WIND BLOWING]

83
00:06:20,298 --> 00:06:22,064
[GASP]

84
00:06:23,364 --> 00:06:26,464
HAIR!
LOTS AND LOTS OF IT.

85
00:06:26,498 --> 00:06:30,331
- THE OLD CRONE WAS RIGHT.
YOU DO HAVE THE SIGHT.

86
00:06:30,364 --> 00:06:33,698
- YOU DID IT!
THE HAIR FOLLOWED YOU,
SO IT CAME HERE!

87
00:06:33,731 --> 00:06:36,798
- KAGOME!
- ARE YOU OK?
- DON'T COME IN!

88
00:06:36,831 --> 00:06:40,864
[GASP]
I'VE GOT TO STOP IT COMING OUT.

89
00:06:45,831 --> 00:06:47,631
AAH! IN FRONT OF YOU!

90
00:06:47,664 --> 00:06:49,964
- WHERE? HERE?
UHH!

91
00:06:49,998 --> 00:06:52,164
HUH...
HUH! YAA!

92
00:06:52,198 --> 00:06:55,031
UHH...UH!
UHH!

93
00:06:55,064 --> 00:06:58,598
- OPEN THE DOOR! NOW!
- KAGOME!

94
00:06:58,631 --> 00:07:01,231
- UHH!
UHH!

95
00:07:03,731 --> 00:07:05,364
- IT REGROWS, EVEN CUT!

96
00:07:05,398 --> 00:07:07,964
PLUS, THERE'S SO MUCH OF IT!

97
00:07:09,864 --> 00:07:11,631
[GROWLING]

98
00:07:11,664 --> 00:07:14,164
[GASP]
- THAT'S IT.

99
00:07:14,631 --> 00:07:18,131
THAT ONE STRAND OF HAIR
CONTROLS IT ALL.

100
00:07:18,164 --> 00:07:19,398
UHH.
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

101
00:07:19,431 --> 00:07:23,298
- HERE. DO YOU SEE IT?
CUT THIS ONE RIGHT HERE.

102
00:07:23,331 --> 00:07:24,864
- WHICH ONE?
THIS ONE?

103
00:07:24,898 --> 00:07:28,898
- INUYASHA CAN'T SEE IT.
I'LL HAVE TO HELP.

104
00:07:28,931 --> 00:07:31,231
- LIKE THIS.

105
00:07:31,264 --> 00:07:32,898
UHH.

106
00:07:34,598 --> 00:07:36,664
- I SEE IT!

107
00:07:36,698 --> 00:07:38,898
UHH!

108
00:07:47,164 --> 00:07:49,764
IT PULLED BACK IN.

109
00:07:50,631 --> 00:07:55,864
- THAT'S NOT GOOD.
YURA'S ALREADY GOT
MY PART OF THE JEWEL,

110
00:07:55,898 --> 00:07:57,898
SO WHY'D SHE DO THIS?

111
00:07:57,931 --> 00:08:03,564
UNLESS IT'S ME AND INUYASHA
SHE'S AFTER.

112
00:08:04,598 --> 00:08:06,498
LET'S GO.
RIGHT NOW.

113
00:08:06,531 --> 00:08:09,664
- BUT I THOUGHT THAT
YOU DIDN'T WANT TO GO BACK.

114
00:08:09,698 --> 00:08:12,798
- I DON'T, BUT I HAVE TO.
- WHAT?

115
00:08:12,831 --> 00:08:16,331
- MOM, SOTA, GRANDPA.

116
00:08:16,364 --> 00:08:19,931
IF I STAY, THEY'LL BE IN DANGER.
HUH?

117
00:08:19,964 --> 00:08:22,898
- IT'S MADE WITH HAIR
OF THE FIRE RAT.

118
00:08:22,931 --> 00:08:24,231
YOU'LL HAVE SOME PROTECTION,
AT LEAST.

119
00:08:24,264 --> 00:08:28,931
- UH, THANK YOU.
- YEAH, WELL, IF YOU WEREN'T
SO WEIRD-LOOKING,

120
00:08:28,964 --> 00:08:30,298
YOU WOULDN'T EVEN NEED IT.

121
00:08:30,331 --> 00:08:31,964
- YOU SHOULD TALK, DOG BOY.

122
00:08:31,998 --> 00:08:34,064
- UHH. YEAH, YEAH, WHATEVER.

123
00:08:34,098 --> 00:08:37,198
YOU READY?
- MM-HMM.

124
00:08:37,231 --> 00:08:38,698
- GRR.

125
00:08:45,498 --> 00:08:48,098
- THEY'LL BE BACK ANY MINUTE.

126
00:08:48,131 --> 00:08:51,764
ONLY WE WON'T LET THEM RUN AWAY
THIS TIME, WILL WE?

127
00:08:51,798 --> 00:08:56,098
[SOBS]
[CHUCKLES]

128
00:08:57,798 --> 00:09:02,964
- HEAR ME, INUYASHA.
KAGOME TRULY IS KIKYO REBORN.

129
00:09:02,998 --> 00:09:05,664
YET THAT WILL AID THEE
BUT LITTLE

130
00:09:05,698 --> 00:09:07,798
IF SHE KNOWS NOT HER OWN POWER.

131
00:09:07,831 --> 00:09:10,198
HELP HER, INUYASHA,
TO FIND HERSELF.

132
00:09:10,231 --> 00:09:13,964
- BE CAREFUL.
THERE'S HAIR INSIDE HERE, TOO.

133
00:09:13,998 --> 00:09:19,264
- UHH. SO YOU'RE SAYING
WHAT YURA IS REALLY AFTER
IS JUST US.

134
00:09:19,298 --> 00:09:21,164
WELL, DUH.
I MEAN, WHY ELSE,

135
00:09:21,198 --> 00:09:24,264
IF SHE ALREADY HAS
MY PIECE OF THE SACRED JEWEL?

136
00:09:24,298 --> 00:09:27,464
- YOUR PIECE OF THE--
HOW DID THAT HAPPEN?

137
00:09:27,498 --> 00:09:29,964
- I CAN SEE A LOT
OF HAIR IN THERE,

138
00:09:29,998 --> 00:09:33,164
BUT ALL WE NEED TO WORRY ABOUT
IS THE MAIN ONE.

139
00:09:33,198 --> 00:09:37,764
IF WE FOLLOW IT,
IT'LL LEAD STRAIGHT TO HER.
I'M SURE OF IT.

140
00:09:37,798 --> 00:09:39,298
THERE!

141
00:09:39,331 --> 00:09:40,131
- GOT IT!

142
00:09:40,164 --> 00:09:42,764
- YE MUST BOTH WORK TOGETHER.

143
00:09:42,798 --> 00:09:45,664
YE NEED KAGOME, INUYASHA,

144
00:09:45,698 --> 00:09:48,198
AND KAGOME, YE NEED HIM.

145
00:09:48,231 --> 00:09:50,831
FORGET YE DIFFERENCES FOR NOW,

146
00:09:50,864 --> 00:09:53,698
AND BE AS ONE.

147
00:09:54,098 --> 00:09:56,098
- UHH!
UHH.

148
00:09:56,131 --> 00:09:59,864
- UH!
- A BONFIRE.

149
00:10:02,564 --> 00:10:06,464
- WHERE ARE THEIR HEADS?
[GRUMBLES]

150
00:10:06,931 --> 00:10:12,364
- THEY'RE GUYS FROM THE VILLAGE,
OR THEIR BODIES, ANYWAY.

151
00:10:12,398 --> 00:10:14,431
LOOKS LIKE THEIR TOPS
CAME CLEAN OFF.

152
00:10:14,464 --> 00:10:19,464
NOW WHAT'S THE MATTER?
I BETTER NOT HEAR YOU
SAY YOU'RE SCARED

153
00:10:19,498 --> 00:10:22,698
OR YOU WANT TO GO HOME.

154
00:10:23,431 --> 00:10:27,231
- ACTUALLY, I THOUGHT
I'D BORROW THESE.

155
00:10:27,264 --> 00:10:32,531
IF WE DON'T STOP HER NOW,
EVEN MORE WILL DIE.

156
00:10:34,331 --> 00:10:38,664
- YOU KNOW YOU'RE NOT GONNA HIT.
WHY BOTHER?

157
00:10:38,698 --> 00:10:40,064
- I JUST NEED PRACTICE.

158
00:10:40,098 --> 00:10:43,731
- PRACTICE?
DON'T YOU MEAN "LEARN"?

159
00:10:43,764 --> 00:10:47,531
- I'LL DO IT.
I REALLY THINK THAT I CAN!

160
00:10:47,564 --> 00:10:50,564
- HMPH. THEN AGAIN,
WHO KNOWS?

161
00:10:50,598 --> 00:10:53,531
MAYBE SHE'LL DO IT AFTER ALL.

162
00:10:53,964 --> 00:10:58,864
- THEY'RE CLOSER.
LOTS CLOSER.

163
00:10:59,064 --> 00:11:03,098
[THUNDER]
- UHH...UHH!

164
00:11:03,664 --> 00:11:05,398
- THEY'RE HERE!
- UHH!

165
00:11:05,431 --> 00:11:08,198
- FROM THE LEFT! FROM THE RIGHT!
- OK! HEY!

166
00:11:08,231 --> 00:11:09,698
- AAH!

167
00:11:11,098 --> 00:11:13,431
THERE'S TOO MANY.
YOU NEED TO HELP.

168
00:11:13,464 --> 00:11:15,931
- ME?
I THOUGHT THAT'S WHY
YOU'RE HERE.

169
00:11:15,964 --> 00:11:18,564
YOU'RE REALLY NOT GOOD FOR MUCH,
ARE YA?

170
00:11:18,598 --> 00:11:19,831
- LEFT! LEFT!
- UHH!

171
00:11:19,864 --> 00:11:22,331
- BEHIND!
UHH! GIVE ME A BREAK!

172
00:11:22,364 --> 00:11:24,731
- UHH!
UHH...

173
00:11:24,764 --> 00:11:26,664
- HUH?

174
00:11:26,698 --> 00:11:29,164
- AAH!
[SCREAM]

175
00:11:29,198 --> 00:11:33,898
- INUYASHA!
- UHH!
HUH?

176
00:11:35,031 --> 00:11:37,398
- A GIANT HAIR BALL?

177
00:11:37,431 --> 00:11:39,664
YURA'S HIDING PLACE.

178
00:11:42,431 --> 00:11:45,298
- OH, MY,
LOOK AT THE CUTE DOGGIE.

179
00:11:45,331 --> 00:11:46,531
[GRUNTING]

180
00:11:46,564 --> 00:11:48,064
- YOU MUST BE INUYASHA.

181
00:11:48,098 --> 00:11:50,864
- AND YOU MUST BE
YURA OF THE HAIR.

182
00:11:50,898 --> 00:11:52,098
HOW'D YOU KNOW MY NAME?

183
00:11:52,131 --> 00:11:54,531
- LET'S JUST SAY
A LITTLE BIRDIE TOLD ME.

184
00:11:54,564 --> 00:11:57,098
EVERYONE'S SAYING
HALF-DEMON INUYASHA

185
00:11:57,131 --> 00:12:00,864
IS PLAYING FETCH WITH SOME
REINCARNATED SHRINE MAIDEN.

186
00:12:00,898 --> 00:12:04,364
- ME?
WITH THAT HALF-WIT HUMAN
DOWN THERE?

187
00:12:04,398 --> 00:12:05,098
NOTHING DOING!

188
00:12:05,131 --> 00:12:08,831
OH?
YOU'RE BOTH HALF-WITS TO ME.

189
00:12:08,864 --> 00:12:12,498
JUST LOOK WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO THE POOR JEWEL.

190
00:12:12,531 --> 00:12:13,398
[GROWLING]

191
00:12:13,431 --> 00:12:16,631
- THAT'S THE JEWEL PIECE
SHE STOLE FROM ME.

192
00:12:16,664 --> 00:12:19,031
- ONCE YOU TWO HERE
HAVE BEEN WRAPPED UP,

193
00:12:19,064 --> 00:12:21,831
I'LL GO AND FIND THE REST
FOR MYSELF.

194
00:12:21,864 --> 00:12:26,031
- YOU, TAKE CARE OF ME?
[GRUNTING]

195
00:12:26,064 --> 00:12:30,098
WHEN THIS IS OVER, YOU'RE GOING
TO WISH YOU'D NEVER MET ME

196
00:12:30,131 --> 00:12:31,798
OR EVER HEARD MY NAME!

197
00:12:31,831 --> 00:12:37,231
UHH! YAA!
AAH! AH!

198
00:12:37,264 --> 00:12:38,231
- UHH.

199
00:12:38,264 --> 00:12:40,731
- NOW WE'RE THE SAME.

200
00:12:41,898 --> 00:12:44,198
[GRUNTING]
AAH!

201
00:12:44,231 --> 00:12:47,598
UHH!
NO, NOT THIS AGAIN.

202
00:12:47,631 --> 00:12:52,731
- SUCH PRETTY HAIR,
BUT YOU REALLY HAVEN'T
CARED FOR IT VERY WELL.

203
00:12:52,764 --> 00:12:57,231
OH, LOOK AT THE SPLIT ENDS.
- GET OFF OF ME!

204
00:13:05,498 --> 00:13:09,298
AAH!
UHH...OHH...

205
00:13:09,331 --> 00:13:11,131
- INUYASHA!

206
00:13:11,164 --> 00:13:13,831
- UHH.

207
00:13:13,864 --> 00:13:15,731
[CHUCKLES]

208
00:13:15,764 --> 00:13:17,264
MMM.

209
00:13:17,298 --> 00:13:21,398
- I'M GOING TO CUT YOU
INTO LITTLE PIECES.

210
00:13:29,634 --> 00:13:30,867
[CHUCKLES]

211
00:13:30,901 --> 00:13:33,401
[SLURP]

212
00:13:33,434 --> 00:13:37,301
I'M GOING TO CUT YOU
INTO LITTLE PIECES.

213
00:13:38,934 --> 00:13:41,967
[GROWLING]
- UHH!

214
00:13:42,001 --> 00:13:43,501
- AH!

215
00:13:46,801 --> 00:13:48,334
- GET HIM DOWN,
RIGHT NOW.

216
00:13:48,367 --> 00:13:50,767
NEXT TIME, I WON'T MISS.
I PROMISE.

217
00:13:50,801 --> 00:13:53,734
- THE GIRL WHO FELL IN THE WELL.

218
00:13:53,767 --> 00:13:55,201
- YOU HEARD ME.

219
00:13:55,234 --> 00:14:00,001
- OOH, I THINK SHE
WANTS YOU BACK, INUYASHA.

220
00:14:00,034 --> 00:14:02,367
WHAT A SWEET WIDDLE DOGGIE
YOU MUST BE.

221
00:14:02,401 --> 00:14:05,634
- I TOLD YOU TO HIDE,
NOT DRAW ATTENTION TO YOURSELF!

222
00:14:05,667 --> 00:14:09,301
- OF COURSE, HER HAIR'S NOT
SO PRETTY AS YOURS, INUYASHA,

223
00:14:09,334 --> 00:14:12,034
BUT THEN...WASTE NOT, WANT NOT.

224
00:14:12,067 --> 00:14:14,301
- NOT SO PRETTY AS HIS, HUH?

225
